source.name: Open Summonses - Active For-Hire-Vehicle (FHV) Drivers
source.description:
List of open summonses written against TLC-licensed drivers.  Only open summonses that have not yet been heard in court are shown – that means that the hearings have not happened and a final decision has not been made in these cases.

File includes Driver License Number, Summons Number and Date Issued, Charges, and current Disposition.
